questions.text: When did your headache start and how long does it typically last?
Can you describe the pain? Is it throbbing, sharp, dull, or something else?
Where exactly is the headache located?
On a scale of 1 to 10, with 10 being the worst pain imaginable, how would you rate your headache?
Are there any other symptoms you are experiencing with the headache, such as nausea, vomiting, sensitivity to light or sound, or changes in vision?
What makes your headache better or worse?
Have you had headaches like this before, or is this a new type of headache for you?
